      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation inputs reviewed by independent analyst; boundary condition application and material assignment verified against protocol documentation.",
      "rationale": "An independent analyst at FDA reviewed all boundary condition definitions, contact pair assignments, and material property inputs against the simulation protocol. No discrepancies identified. Achieved level meets required level."
